title: Laurel & Hardy - Flying deuces.avi
description:
SYNOPSIS:

Ollie is in love with a woman. When he find out that she is already married, 
he tries to kill himself. 
Of course, the suicide is prevented and the boys join the Foreign Legion to get away from their troubles. 
Eventually, they are arrested for trying to desert the Legion and escape the firing squad by stealing a plane.



Director: A. Edward Sutherland
Producer: Boris Morros
Production Company: RKO Radio Pictures, Inc
Audio/Visual: sound, black & white
